8	1033 program - Wikipedia	In the United States, the 1033 Program transfers excess military equipment to  civilian law enforcement agencies. As of 2014, 8,000 local law enforcement  agencies participated in the program that has transferred $5.1 billion in military  material from the Department of Defense to law enforcement agencies since  1997.	https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/1033_program
